1
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:24,719
Stop it!

2
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:26,640
What are you doing?

3
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:28,719
My lord.

4
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,000
You're finally back.

5
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,680
Ning Chen defied his elders.

6
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,239
And dumped filth all over Gan'er.

7
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,879
Father, Mother is right.

8
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,840
You can't keep favoring Ning Chen.

9
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:41,799
Chen'er.

10
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,560
Is what they said all true?

11
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,560
Yes, it's true.

12
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,719
But before Lord Ning passes judgment,

13
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,959
shouldn't you find out why this happened?

14
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:52,159
Ning Gan and Ning Xing trashed my room.

15
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,480
They turned a fine room into a pigsty.

16
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,879
Was I wrong to fight back?

17
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:59,040
These two unfilial sons!

18
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:02,000
Why provoke Ning Chen for no reason?

19
00:02:02,879 --> 00:02:04,400
If His Majesty learns of this,

20
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,439
the entire Ning household is doomed.

21
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:08,719
Kneel.

22
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:13,919
Hey, Ning Chen,

23
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,879
didn't you hear what Father said?

24
00:02:16,039 --> 00:02:17,000
Get on your knees, now.

25
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,000
I meant you two fools, kneel down!

26
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,479
Father.

27
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,240
We didn't do anything wrong.

28
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,560
That's right, Father.

29
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,960
We truly meant well for Ning Chen.

30
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,080
We brought men to check his room for rats.

31
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:37,680
I...

32
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:39,319
You think I don't know?

33
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,719
It's because Ning Chen is now in favor.

34
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:44,479
So you scheme every way to trip him up.

35
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:46,599
Can you really not tolerate him?

36
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,560
Ning Ziming!

37
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,400
What on earth are you doing?

38
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,319
Ever since you brought him home,

39
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,960
you've grown harsher toward me and my sons.

40
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:55,039
Could it be

41
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:57,000
that you want to drive us away,

42
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,159
so this bastard can inherit our estate?

43
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,199
Shut your mouth!

44
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,400
Foolish woman, what do you know?

45
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,879
Every time I pushed back before,

46
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,240
Ning Ziming would always concede.

47
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:08,560
Why is he so stubborn this time?

48
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,840
You've got some nerve, Ning Ziming.

49
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,840
Have you forgotten how you rose to power?

50
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:14,520
Smashing his room is nothing.

51
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:16,159
Even if I burned it to the ground,

52
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:17,080
so what?

53
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,439
As long as I'm here,

54
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:19,840
no one will split this family's fortune.

55
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,039
Wait, you...

56
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:23,000
Chief Eunuch Quan arrives!

57
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:29,280
Chief Eunuch Quan, what brings you here?

58
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,759
This guy is the Chief Eunuch?

59
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:34,039
The head of all eunuchs in the realm.

60
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:35,840
Then doesn't that mean the old man is...

61
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,000
Hey, kid.

62
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,400
Surprised?

63
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,319
Caught off guard?

64
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:49,319
Not really that surprised.

65
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,879
Your edict for the Imperial Inspectorate.

66
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,759
I won't bother reading it aloud.

67
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,599
The Imperial Inspectorate?

68
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,319
His Majesty values Ning Chen so highly?

69
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:06,039
This...

70
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,960
When did this bastard

71
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,159
become this capable?

72
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,800
Chief Eunuch, you arrived at the perfect time.

73
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:13,439
So that means

74
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:16,680
I'm now an official of the court.

75
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:19,439
Though only a Silver Robe,

76
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:22,199
I'm a genuine court official nonetheless.

77
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,680
So if someone

78
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:26,519
ransacked a court official's residence,

79
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,319
according to our dynasty's law,

80
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:30,639
how should they be punished?

81
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,519
By Da Xuan Law,

82
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,560
those who trespass in private homes

83
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,399
and steal others' property

84
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,680
shall receive fifty strokes of the cane,

85
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:41,079
and be imprisoned for one year.

86
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,040
For severe cases,

87
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,439
they shall be branded as slaves

88
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,879
and exiled three thousand li.

89
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:54,279
You two young masters,

90
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,560
who gets 50 strokes and a year in prison,

91
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:01,360
and who gets branded and exiled 3,000 li?

92
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,879
Decide amongst yourselves.

93
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:06,879
I happen to have a good idea.

94
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:09,839
You're off to the Imperial Inspectorate,

95
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:12,000
why not take them along?

96
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:14,639
I've heard the Imperial Inspectorate's

97
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,959
Zhao Prison is utterly terrifying.

98
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:20,279
Ghosts of the wrongfully dead linger on.

99
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,759
Often, the wailing of ghosts

100
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,079
when the skies darken

101
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,279
can clearly be heard.

102
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:26,959
No.

103
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,959
I don't want to go.

104
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,839
Mother, not the Imperial Inspectorate!

105
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,920
Father, Father, save me!

106
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:34,839
I can't go.

107
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:35,920
So now you know fear?

108
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:37,800
What were you thinking causing trouble?

109
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,199
Mother.

110
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:40,959
I can't go.

111
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,959
The Palace Examination is coming up.

112
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:43,680
If I go, my official career is finished.

113
00:05:44,279 --> 00:05:44,920
Don't worry.

114
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,720
With your mother here today,

115
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,680
let's see who dares lay a hand on you.

116
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,480
I really did underestimate you.

117
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:54,279
Sneaking into the Imperial Inspectorate.

118
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,639
Don't you forget,

119
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:58,319
Gan'er and Xing'er's grandfather

120
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:00,480
is the current Left Chancellor.

121
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:03,279
A petty little official like you

122
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,920
trying to throw your weight around?

123
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,399
You're nowhere near worthy.

124
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:10,879
What did you just say?

125
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,399
Imperial Inspectorate serves His Majesty.

126
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,360
How dare you?

127
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,480
Truly the Left Chancellor's daughter.

128
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,480
What audacity.

129
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,079
But the words you just spoke,

130
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:21,600
at the very least,

131
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:24,120
disregard authority and offend the crown.

132
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:26,600
At worst, that's treason.

133
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,560
Unforgivable.

134
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,199
Punishable by death of nine generations.

135
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:32,759
And saying this before the wise, valiant,

136
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:34,560
the brilliant Chief Eunuch Quan?

137
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,560
Chief, you heard every word, didn't you?

138
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:38,639
Every single word.

139
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,160
Chief Eunuch,

140
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,040
it's a misunderstanding.

141
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:43,279
A misunderstanding. You see,

142
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,560
my wife was just protecting her sons,

143
00:06:45,759 --> 00:06:46,560
and spoke without thinking.

144
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:52,160
Chen'er,

145
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:53,839
we're all family.

146
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,279
Why act this way?

147
00:06:55,519 --> 00:06:56,519
Who's your family?

148
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,959
Don't try to claim kinship now.

149
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,160
I'm not part of your nine generations.

150
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,240
Father,

151
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:08,480
how can he say such treasonous things?

152
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,240
Gan'er.

153
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:13,439
Look at the mess you've made!

154
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,160
Apologize to Chen'er at once!

155
00:07:15,519 --> 00:07:16,000
What's it gonna be?

156
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,560
Want to rot in prison, is that it?

157
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,399
Ning Ziming,

158
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:20,279
you shut your mouth too.

159
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,639
Defying imperial authority?

160
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,560
Forget about me,

161
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:23,360
even if your father-in-law came,

162
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,360
he couldn't bear the consequences.

163
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,160
And you.

164
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,560
Think I forgot about you?

165
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:31,360
Get on your knees.

166
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,279
Apologize to Ning Chen.

167
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:34,839
Now!

168
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,160
The Left Chancellor holds great power.

169
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,920
His proteges are everywhere.

170
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,519
Just make your point.

171
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,399
And quit while you're ahead.

172
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,160
Quit, quit, quit.

173
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,319
Ning Chen.

174
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,480
Look, you're all brothers.

175
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,040
Brothers fighting brothers...

176
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:00,920
will make us a laughingstock.

177
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:01,680
How about this?

178
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,519
Today, just bear with them.

179
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:04,439
And later,

180
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:06,600
I'll discipline these two properly.

181
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:09,079
Cat got your tongues?

182
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,639
Bas...

183
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:14,319
No.

184
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:15,639
Fourth brother.

185
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:16,879
Enough.

186
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,040
No need for apologies.

187
00:08:19,519 --> 00:08:20,439
You pretend to apologize,

188
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:21,439
I pretend to forgive.

189
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,680
We're all quite busy.

190
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,920
No need to act out this brotherly love.

191
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,959
However, Lord Ning,

192
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:32,919
those two trashed my room.

193
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,440
Well...

194
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:37,039
Your room's furnishings were old anyway.

195
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,360
I've long wanted to replace them.

196
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:40,039
I've just been busy with official duties

197
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,840
and hadn't gotten around to it.

198
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:41,960
Don't worry.

199
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:44,000
I'll have everything replaced right away.

200
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:51,559
I soon start at the Imperial Inspectorate.

201
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,759
I finally landed a proper job.

202
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:56,639
Bribes up and down are unavoidable.

203
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:01,399
No problem.

204
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,879
I'll have a thousand taels of silver sent

205
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,919
to your room right away.

206
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,159
So readily?

207
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,320
Seems my vision wasn't grand enough.

208
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,120
I asked for too little.

209
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,320
My lord.

210
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:17,879
Old General Chen awaits Ning Chen outside.

211
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,559
How dare you!

212
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,840
Dare you utter the Fourth Master's name?

213
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,240
Listen well, all of you.

214
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:25,360
If anyone again disrespects their superior,

215
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:27,080
they'll all be severely punished.

216
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,399
Is that clear?

217
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:29,879
Yes.

218
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:33,480
Congratulations, Silver Robe Ning.

219
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,159
Just an empty title.

220
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:37,960
Many thanks, Chief Eunuch Quan.

221
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,279
I'll repay you handsomely later.

222
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,000
You scared me half to death.

223
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,519
I appreciate the thought.

224
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:47,360
I still have urgent matters to attend to.

225
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,799
I'll take my leave now.

226
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,720
I'll see the Chief Eunuch out.

227
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:51,519
And see what Old General Chen wants.

228
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,039
After you.

229
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,440
Farewell, Chief Eunuch Quan.

230
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:56,960
Get up, quickly.

231
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:00,679
You all saw that clearly, didn't you?

232
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,399
It's not that I'm favoring Ning Chen.

233
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:03,360
It's just that now,

234
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,639
Ning Chen has caught His Majesty's eye.

235
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:07,639
You all... this...

236
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,159
Stay clear of him from now on.

237
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:10,919
Honestly...

238
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,080
I never expected

239
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:18,360
that Ning Chen would have such fortune.

240
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,120
I'm puzzled.

241
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:23,240
How did he ever meet His Majesty?

242
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:24,600
Mother.

243
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,559
Now he's in the Imperial Inspectorate,

244
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,320
after how we treated him before,

245
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,840
will he... will he take revenge on us?

246
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,080
Yes, Mother.

247
00:10:32,399 --> 00:10:32,919
What's there to panic about?

248
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,200
A bastard will always be a bastard.

249
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,600
He'll never amount to anything refined.

250
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,080
Besides, he's merely a Silver Robe.

251
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,519
You go wash up properly in a bit.

252
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,000
You two come with me to see Grandfather.

253
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:46,840
There's a step here.

254
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:47,600
Don't trip.

255
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:48,519
Here, buddy.

256
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,320
Play with this for a while.

257
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,159
Greetings, Old General Chen.

258
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:57,879
Greetings, Chief Eunuch Quan.

259
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:01,159
Chief Eunuch Quan came to read the edict.

260
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:04,679
This boosts Ning Chen's standing at home.

261
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,279
I am merely following orders.

262
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:10,399
His Majesty awaits my report.

263
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:11,879
I take my leave.

264
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:12,679
Farewell.

265
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:18,120
Old General bought a carriage?

266
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:20,919
What's the act today?

267
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,080
What nonsense are you spouting?

268
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,039
You little brat.

269
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:27,799
A few days ago, you helped me out.

270
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:28,639
So today,

271
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:31,000
I picked out a special gift for you.

272
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,320
Bring it over.

273
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:37,200
I had this horse brought from Persia

274
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,320
just for you.

275
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,000
It can run a thousand li a day.

276
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,559
This horse is called

277
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,320
Black Qilin.

278
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,840
Black Qilin.

279
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,960
Today, I'm giving it to you.

280
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:47,639
Wow.

281
00:11:47,759 --> 00:11:48,639
A foreign steed.

282
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,840
What's a foreign steed?

283
00:11:51,279 --> 00:11:51,799
It means a forei--

284
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,840
Anyway, it's a fine horse.

285
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:55,879
A fine horse.

286
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,799
Truly a fine horse.

287
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,519
You're being awfully courteous today.

288
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:04,399
Don't tell me

289
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:07,320
you're up to no good?

290
00:12:07,639 --> 00:12:08,360
Nonsense!

291
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:11,159
I simply admire you, that's all.

292
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,279
Take this gift

293
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:14,399
and treasure it well.

294
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:17,240
A true man should ride against the wind,

295
00:12:17,399 --> 00:12:19,480
die in battle, wrapped in horsehide.

296
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:23,360
Not like me,

297
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,879
stuck in this tiny little place.

298
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,519
Dying in battle, wrapped in horsehide,

299
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,159
that's the end you truly seek, right?

300
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,639
Not like the way things are now.

301
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:41,039
At your age,

302
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,120
spare me the brooding act.

303
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,279
Maybe one day I'll surprise you.

304
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,879
I'd be lucky if you didn't scare me.

305
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:50,080
Give this horse a name.

306
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,480
What does this beauty want to be called?

307
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:09,799
Xishi?

308
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:11,399
Zhaojun?

309
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,240
Guifei?

310
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,000
Diaochan?

311
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:20,879
Oh, you want to be called Diaochan?

312
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:21,360
Alright.

313
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,600
Then from now on, your name is Diaochan.

314
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,320
Diaochan. What a fine name.

315
00:13:28,159 --> 00:13:29,120
She chose it herself.

316
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,240
As long as the child likes it.

317
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,639
Now, back to business.

318
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,960
I meant to put you in the War Ministry.

319
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:36,399
You have the makings of a general.

320
00:13:36,759 --> 00:13:38,679
You should be shining on the battlefield.

321
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,720
As you're in the Imperial Inspectorate,

322
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:43,919
he must have his reasons.

323
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:45,600
Today,

324
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:47,960
allow me to offer you some advice.

325
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,919
Please speak, Old General.

326
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:52,440
First.

327
00:13:53,519 --> 00:13:54,919
You have a free-spirited nature,

328
00:13:55,399 --> 00:13:58,080
unwilling to be bound by worldly rules.

329
00:13:58,399 --> 00:13:59,480
But toward the royal family,

330
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:02,120
you must maintain due respect.

331
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:05,159
Second.

332
00:14:05,759 --> 00:14:07,720
Imperial Inspectorate serves His Majesty.

333
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:10,360
Keep your distance from other officials.

334
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,559
Never give them grounds for gossip.

335
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:14,720
Third.

336
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,440
Imperial Inspectorate oversees officials,

337
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:20,440
and major cases across the nation.

338
00:14:20,919 --> 00:14:22,480
You must hold fast to your principles.

339
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:27,559
Never let power or wealth blind your eyes.

340
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:32,360
Thank you for your guidance, Old General.

341
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:34,360
I will surely stay true to myself

342
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:35,200
and never forget my original intent.

343
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:37,559
Just remember it. That's all.

344
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:38,840
Alright then.

345
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,919
You and I, you rascal, are bound by fate.

346
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:44,919
Visit my residence often from now on.

347
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,159
I won't serve you fake wine.

348
00:14:47,639 --> 00:14:49,440
Then I'll only bring peanuts.

349
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:52,720
Even stingier than me.

350
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,080
Head back.

351
00:14:57,039 --> 00:14:58,000
Take good care of the horse.

352
00:14:58,120 --> 00:14:59,120
Don't let it grow thin on me.

353
00:14:59,279 --> 00:15:00,000
I won't.

354
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:02,279
With me, it will get fatter than you.

355
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,639
Rather than being the royal hound,

356
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:13,200
I'd much prefer to head into battle.

357
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,120
After all, I was once a soldier.

358
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,279
The battlefield is my true stage.

359
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,679
When you and I join forces someday,

360
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:24,120
we'll surely shine brilliantly.

361
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:32,919
The fate of the world is yet undecided.

362
00:15:33,559 --> 00:15:36,000
You and I are both dark horses.

